    • createResult

      public static ResultPacket createResult​(ResultType resultType, boolean result, java.lang.String msg)
      Creates a ResultPacket from the given information. The usage of this method as createResult(resultType,result,msg) is equivelent to createResult(resultType.id,result,msg)
      Parameters:
      resultType - the ResultType of the packet
      result - was the request successful?
      msg - a message included with the result
      Returns:
      a ResultPacket from the given information
      See Also:
      createResult(int, boolean, java.lang.String), ResultPacket(common.networking.packet.packets.result.ResultType, boolean, java.lang.String)

    • createResult

      public static ResultPacket createResult​(int resultType, boolean result, java.lang.String msg)
      Creates a ResultPacket from the given information. If msg is null and result is false, msg will be made ""
      Parameters:
      resultType - the result type of the packet
      result - was the request successful?
      msg - a message included with the result
      Returns:
      a ResultPacket from the given information
      See Also:
      createResult(common.networking.packet.packets.result.ResultType, boolean, java.lang.String), ResultPacket(int, boolean, java.lang.String)
